  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A frustrating jump action game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the goal using only jumps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action Difficulty: ★★★☆☆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frustration Level: ★★★★★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Story-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An emoji wandering in a broken world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guided by a mysterious voice saying, \"Aim for space to escape,\" the emoji jumps toward the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mysterious voice insults you every time you fail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you endure the verbal abuse and reach space?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Controls-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2638350/extras/e97aece0a4c5a45b92090bdb79470393.avif?t=1735265719\" width=650 height=316 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump: Left-click or Space key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2638350/extras/84c8f67e7569d66da9fbfcb348bc38e6.avif?t=1735265719\" width=650 height=316 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colliding with walls reverses the left and right directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESC: Show menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the platforms with jumps and aim for space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The subtitles and UI in the DEMO version are available only in English and Japanese.</p>",
